// BUnit test example: TestCase subclass with assertion methods (ADR 0014 Phase 2)

TestCase subclass: ArithmeticTest

  testAddition =>
    self assert: (1 + 2) equals: 3

  testSubtraction =>
    self assert: (5 - 3) equals: 2

  testNegation =>
    self assert: (0 - 1) equals: -1

  testEquality =>
    self assert: (2 + 2 == 4)

  testDeny =>
    self deny: (1 == 2)
